// Genuine Stylus so the Stylus preprocessor must run for this to compile:
// a Stylus `$variable` with conditional `?=` assignment and indentation-based
// (brace-less) rule syntax, neither valid plain CSS. Mirrors Vite's
// playground/css/stylus.styl (`$color ?= blue` then `.stylus\n  color $color`).
$color ?= blue

.stylus
  color $color
